Package nescent.phylogeoref.reader

Interface Summary
MetadataReader Superclass for all metadata reader class.
TreeReader Superclass for all tree file readers.
 

Class Summary
CSVMetadataReader Reads metadata from a CSV file.
GrandUnifiedReader Reads the raw, skeletal tree structure from a treeFile.
MultiFormatReader  
NeXMLEngine Provides methods that can construct a Phylogeny object from a Tree or Network.
NeXMLReader Takes an NeXML file.
PhylogenyKitchen Takes a raw, crude phylogenetic tree and metadata from a secondary file and converts it into a cooked, full-fledged phylogenetic tree.
PhylogenyMould Each labeled phylogeny node has a mould associated with it to contain additional metadata that forester library's implementation cannot accomodate.
TextMetadataReader Reads metadata from a text file.
UniversalMetadataReader Reads metadata from all types of files.
UniversalTreeReader Reads all kinds of input tree files.
